489
00:27:15,700 --> 00:27:16,540
Noon,

490
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:18,580
nang mangyari ang insidente ni Gao Ying,

491
00:27:19,140 --> 00:27:21,220
Si Huo Kaiming noon
ang opisyal ng kaligtasan sa tungkulin.

492
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:24,300
Hindi bababa sa, ang pamamaraan
ng pagsunog ng katawan ay pareho.

493
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:25,380
Akala ko,

494
00:27:25,380 --> 00:27:26,380
pwede bang...

495
00:27:27,340 --> 00:27:28,200
Direktor Chen,

496
00:27:28,210 --> 00:27:31,020
tungkol sa aplikasyon
para muling buksan ang kaso ni Gao Ying,

497
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:33,380
sabi ng municipal PSB
kailangan pa nila ng mga supporting materials.

498
00:27:33,980 --> 00:27:36,300
Kailangan kong bumalik at hilahin
ang mga orihinal na file mula noon.

499
00:27:38,140 --> 00:27:39,100
Sige.

500
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:40,660
Maghihintay ako ng pag-unlad sa iyong pagtatapos.

501
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,140
Direktor Chen,

502
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:48,300
please don't mind me ask.

503
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:49,160
Sige na.

504
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,140
Ngayong gising na si Hui,

505
00:27:50,420 --> 00:27:52,480
at maayos ang takbo ng mga bagay
sa pagitan mo ng iyong asawa,

506
00:27:52,820 --> 00:27:54,060
bakit pa ulitin ang bagay na ito?

507
00:27:57,420 --> 00:27:58,580
Speaking of our relationship,

508
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:01,220
Ding Yue at Gao Ying

509
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,580
besties sila noon.

510
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:06,500
Kahit maraming taon na ang lumipas,

511
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:09,060
kung hindi ko ito lilinawin,

512
00:28:09,060 --> 00:28:10,660
Lagi kong mararamdaman

513
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:11,660
parang nabigo ako kay Gao Ying

514
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,860
at nabigo ang aking sarili,

515
00:28:13,860 --> 00:28:15,700
lalo na ang pagiging pulis ngayon.

516
00:28:18,660 --> 00:28:19,540
naiintindihan ko.

517
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:22,420
Hahanap ako ng ibang paraan.

518
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:23,260
