540
00:29:10,580 --> 00:29:11,570
Kailangan niyang manatiling aktibo.

541
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:13,670
Bumalik ka para magpa-check-up
kung may mga problema.

542
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:16,020
Salamat, Doktor.

543
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:16,990
Narinig kong sinabi mo yan

544
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,060
