553
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:31,820
Madali.

554
00:29:32,820 --> 00:29:33,940
Mag ingat kayong dalawa.

555
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:34,780
Naiintindihan mo, Mrs. Chen.

556
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,620
