577
00:30:16,910 --> 00:30:17,940
- Okay.
- Kukunin ko ito.

578
00:30:17,940 --> 00:30:20,580
Tara uwi na tayo, magluluto ako
isang bagay na masarap para sa iyo.

579
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:21,660
Okay.

580
00:30:21,660 --> 00:30:22,620
- Tara na.
- Tara na.

581
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:24,620
Ang ganda talaga ng araw ngayon.

582
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:31,700
Tignan mo yan.

583
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,940
- Tatay.
- Naghihintay siya sa pintuan.

584
00:30:34,050 --> 00:30:34,930
Tingnan mo.

585
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:36,360
Panganay kong apo, bumalik ka na.

586
00:30:36,740 --> 00:30:37,740
ako

587
