615
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:23,980
Tara na.

616
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:25,500
Seryoso.

617
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:27,070
Akala ko talaga may mali.

618
00:31:31,020 --> 00:31:31,980
- Dumikit.
- Dumikit.

619
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:32,920
- Manok.
- Manok.

620
00:31:35,140 --> 00:31:36,880
