tumatakbo siya pabalik-balik.

668
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:54,540
Masakit panoorin.

669
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:55,700
ayos lang ako.

670
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:56,550
Ginang Chen,

671
