698
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:56,740
Eto, may baso ka.

699
00:34:00,580 --> 00:34:02,420
Miss Chen, inumin mo itong juice.

700
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,700
Songge, ako na mismo ang gagawa.

701
