708
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:15,720
- Maligayang pagbabalik.
- Salamat, Tatay.

709
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:18,500
Nais kong mabilis kang bumalik sa kalusugan, Hui.

710
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:20,540
Salamat, Lolo. Salamat, Nanay.

711
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:22,180
Tatay, hiling ko rin sa iyo ang mabuting kalusugan.

712
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:23,580
Mabuti. Magandang kalusugan sa lahat.

713
00:34:23,580 --> 00:34:24,580
Magandang kalusugan sa lahat.

714
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:26,500
Dad, dahan-dahan.

715
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,660
Mrs. Chen,
masarap ang mga gulay na ito.

716
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:29,820
- Hindi masyadong maalat?
- Hindi.

717
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:31,110
